    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>One of this creature's special attacks is particularly difficult to resist.</em><br /><br /><strong>Prerequisites</strong><br />Special attack.<br /><br /><strong>Benefits</strong><br />Choose one of the creature's special attacks. Add +2 to the DC for all saving throws against the special attack on which the creature focuses.</p>\n<p><strong>Special<br /></strong>A creature can gain this feat multiple times. Its effects do not stack. Each time the creature takes the feat, it applies to a different special attack.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Usage</strong></p>\n<p>Rename ability to include the name of the special attack affected. Add a note / increase the DC by +2 for the special attack.</p>",
